name: Mistress of the Earth
description: Woman is the beginning and the End of life, she is the Mother Nature, not obeying anyone, willful and wise. And the fierce Kali, the slashing head of Ignorance and Greed. This is a cruel warrior and a generous Mistress. Deity manifested in everything and unmanifested, secret, hidden. A force that can be revealed in everyone who has the courage to challenge, be disobedient. This is Lilith, the first rebel, Astarte, the goddess of fertility, Inanna, who never dies, Babalon the Scarlet Wife and Baphomet, the Lady of the Earth. To her by right belongs the Sickle of the Moon. She is a Heaven and a Hell. Here is her throne, her realm, her priestess and her enemy
